label: XL Recordings
description:
Bashy drumfunk, jiggly big room tech and scratchy UKG mutations from the brothers Overmono

Following up their Fabric mix, the duo cycle from the splashy breakbeat stepper ‘Cash Romantic’ whereas ‘Fortune’ works up a detuned R&B ditty, ‘Bone Mics’ trades in bilgy UKG, and ‘Phosycon’ slows down to a skudgy swagger offset between Four Tet and Joy O.
